data.description: ??PRICE DROP!! With 0.37 of an acre, run the block in this 4,011 sq ft home. Southside living with all the southern sunshine pours into every newly installed window of this charming home. Don’t worry about the temperature outside, as this home features a zone ac system that allows different temperatures to run simultaneously in various rooms. If that’s not cool enough, take a dip in your pool featured out back in your plushly green large yard with view of the beautiful fountain and pool house. After working up your appetite, get prepared to cook in your chef style gourmet kitchen with built in features. Whether they are home for the holidays or home for good, everyone has as room as this home has 5 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms. Come take a look and bring your ideas as she’s ready for renovations and more. Call you favorite realtor today.
